data.description: Welcome home to this LIKE NEW Energy Efficient Brite Home that is MOVE-IN READY! This home is loaded with upgrades throughout. Per the builder, some of these features include: Spray foam insulation and double pane windows that create an airtight seal, LED lighting, energy efficient water heater, insulated ductwork, high performance HVAC units and more. This home has a spacious open floor plan. Three sizeable bedrooms plus a bonus room that can be used as an office or play area. The kitchen is any hosts dream with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and 42” real wood soft close cabinets with an elegant island overlooking the family room with custom built entertaining center with built in electric fireplace. There is NO CARPET in this home, luxury plank flooring and crown molding throughout. Primary suite is equipped with beautiful tray ceiling, and master bath has soaking tub with separate stand-up shower. Oversized back covered lanai perfect for outside entertaining. All furniture is before offered for purchase separately.
